data.description: Beautiful home in King of Arms! Enter into foyer with hardwood floors leading to formal dining and formal living rms. Spacious and completely updated kitchen with huge center island & dining space are open to the family rm w/gas fp. Laundry rm & a half bath complete the first floor. Upstairs, you will find laminate hardwood floors throughout, a lg primary suite w/walk in closet and full bathrm; 3 more bdrms & another full bath. Partially finished LL with large rec room, wet bar, flex rm and full bath. Tons of storage in the 3 car, extra deep, heated garage! New paint in almost every room of the house and new carpet in the family rm and stairs! This home is a show stopper and a MUST see! Schedule your showing today!
